g.text: So... what's your problem with Eleanor, anyway?

g.title: j5866127

g.title: j3363110322
g.text: We all wound up as monsters
But that bruja delights in what we've become
Gets a sick glee out of messing about in my head
Sees too much and thinks she knows everything

g.title: j504918271
g.text: ¿Ay, sí?
And why is that?
Did the bruja send you to talk to me

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j3026324705
g.text: Even if she never devolves into the Techrot
And she stays like she is now I don't care
That bruja still enjoys this shit too much

g.title: j2168176454
g.text: No, she didn't. I'm here on my own accord.

g.title: j2248941100
g.text: It doesn't matter if she did or not, I still think you should ease up.

g.title: j3536472108
g.text: Just because she embraces what's happened to her doesn't make her a bad person.

g.title: j2594380578
g.text: I just don't think you're being fair to her, Lettie.

g.title: j2550095532
g.text: And why should I
She could snap at any point and devolve into the Techrot
And even if she doesn't that bruja enjoys all this too much
We're all monsters now but the difference is she LIKES it

g.title: j1369215390
g.text: It's one thing to accept it
It's another thing to enjoy it
And she can learn to not be a metiche and stay the hell out of my DAMN head

g.title: j3616292511
g.text: ¿Ay, sí, verdad?
Do tell

g.title: j1926457694
g.text: She's one of your teammates, Lettie. And like it or not, you're stuck with her. You need to work on letting go of your grudges.

g.title: j2618398285
g.text: She's lost her voice. She has to listen to everybody's thoughts all the time. She gets weird flashes of things she doesn't understand.

g.title: j1813807176
g.text: Sure, sure
How well is that working out for you, babas
Have you forgiven all your grudges

g.title: j1558313511
g.text: And she's the one who is the closest to the Techrot. Can you imagine what that must feel like, to hear them all the time?

g.title: j4288591640
g.text: And she has all of YOU treating her like she's the real monster. Can you imagine what that must feel like?

g.title: j734077835
g.text: Check boolean LettieReligion2

g.title: j1395482136
g.text: That is exactly the problem
You keep making my arguments for me, babas

g.title: j1369033558
g.text: Can you blame her for meeting that kind of disgust with defiance instead of shame?

g.title: j1517332719
